379
00:22:12,113 --> 00:22:13,315
It is impossible?

380
00:22:14,636 --> 00:22:17,022
You will find out soon.

381
00:22:18,183 --> 00:22:19,319
It is possible...

382
00:22:20,534 --> 00:22:22,559
to progress for a short moment.

383
00:22:24,183 --> 00:22:25,818
But politics reverts...

384
00:22:26,605 --> 00:22:28,306
to its original position.

385
00:22:30,511 --> 00:22:32,703
So soon you will realize...

386
00:22:34,964 --> 00:22:36,964
that you had dreamed of...

387
00:22:40,636 --> 00:22:41,971
an unattainable dream.

388
00:22:49,799 --> 00:22:50,861
Wait.

389
00:22:54,870 --> 00:22:56,331
Wait a moment.

390
00:23:03,705 --> 00:23:05,806
We can progress for a short
moment...

391
00:23:07,863 --> 00:23:09,499
but will fall back eventually?

392
00:23:10,956 --> 00:23:11,849
Then why...

393
00:23:15,175 --> 00:23:16,965
did you help me?

394
00:23:17,932 --> 00:23:19,302
If you think...

395
00:23:19,683 --> 00:23:21,748
it will be of no use?

396
00:23:23,269 --> 00:23:24,132
Why?

397
00:23:33,473 --> 00:23:34,577
That is...

398
00:23:37,214 --> 00:23:39,398
The reason is that...

399
00:24:01,659 --> 00:24:02,709
Min Jin Heon.

400
00:24:07,636 --> 00:24:09,019
The man who entrusted Yoon Yeong...

401
00:24:09,233 --> 00:24:10,718
did not come for the money?

402
00:24:11,081 --> 00:24:12,193
Not yet.

403
00:24:13,128 --> 00:24:15,825
