and that is why I volunteered.

404
00:24:16,409 --> 00:24:18,409
- But for some reason...
- Can we get in touch with him?

405
00:24:19,566 --> 00:24:22,861
He is an itinerant merchant
who does not have an address.

406
00:24:22,863 --> 00:24:24,478
Then we do not know where he lives?

407
00:24:46,441 --> 00:24:47,780
We will find a boat soon.

408
00:24:47,782 --> 00:24:49,229
Then we will go to Qing and...

409
00:24:57,214 --> 00:24:59,109
You deserted me too.

410
00:25:00,589 --> 00:25:01,448
Did you not?

411
00:25:05,253 --> 00:25:07,340
I was easy to take advantage of
because I was dumb and pathetic?

412
00:25:08,714 --> 00:25:09,694
That is nonsense.

413
00:25:10,691 --> 00:25:13,687
Did you really think I would not
know how other people thought of me?

414
00:25:14,956 --> 00:25:16,940
Everyone laughed at me
and mocked me from behind.

415
00:25:17,558 --> 00:25:19,051
They treated me like
an insect.

416
00:25:20,222 --> 00:25:22,173
But in case I became king,

417
00:25:22,796 --> 00:25:23,883
they flattered me...

418
00:25:24,055 --> 00:25:25,827
in front of me. Am I wrong?

419
00:25:27,644 --> 00:25:28,967
But it did not matter.

420
00:25:29,901 --> 00:25:31,422
I could just become king.

421
00:25:32,230 --> 00:25:33,140
When I became the king,

422
00:25:33,698 --> 00:25:35,450
they would not laugh at me
even from behind.

423
00:25:36,816 --> 00:25:37,699
And you...

424
00:25:41,784 --> 00:25:44,204
would hold me sincerely.

425
00:25:51,542 --> 00:25:53,849
I am sorry.

426
00:25:58,761 --> 00:26:00,590
The one who made you like this...

427
00:26:02,433 --> 00:26:03,435
is me.

428
00:26:06,597 --> 00:26:08,999
So give me a chance too.

429
00:26:10,277 --> 00:26:13,095
So I can forgive at least
one person...

430
00:26:14,784 --> 00:26:16,051
just like I was...

431
00:26:17,042 --> 00:26:18,545
forgiven by someone.

432
00:26:28,119 --> 00:26:29,561
Tomorrow at Hall of Convenience,

433
00:26:30,612 --> 00:26:32,532
the senior officials will probably
not show up.

434
00:26:33,062 --> 00:26:33,844
If that happens,

435
00:26:34,682 --> 00:26:36,218
I will issue the order.

436
00:26:37,175 --> 00:26:38,893
I will do as you say.

437
00:26:42,112 --> 00:26:44,000
Thank you for your decision,
Chief Justice.

438
00:26:44,995 --> 00:26:45,980
From tomorrow,

439
00:26:46,691 --> 00:26:48,239
it will be war again.

440
00:26:48,909 --> 00:26:50,832
Why do you not get some sleep?

441
00:26:51,620 --> 00:26:54,450
- No, I have things to...
- It is because...

442
00:26:56,800 --> 00:26:58,145
I am tired.

443
00:27:00,816 --> 00:27:01,877
Oh, I am sorry.

444
00:27:02,270 --> 00:27:03,691
I did not think of that.

445
00:27:03,691 --> 00:27:05,141
You are working your old subject...

446
00:27:05,691 --> 00:27:07,604
too harshly.

447
00:27:23,552 --> 00:27:27,235
Excuse me. May I see Court Lady Heo
for a moment?

448
00:27:30,253 --> 00:27:31,140
Yeo Ji.

449
00:27:33,761 --> 00:27:36,640
Why are you at the palace
at this hour?

450
00:27:43,472 --> 00:27:44,397
Really?

451
00:27:45,300 --> 00:27:48,122
You made these snacks just for me?

452
00:27:49,401 --> 00:27:51,415
You seemed to be working late,

453
00:27:51,770 --> 00:27:53,996
so I was going to give it
to Court Lady Heo.

454
00:27:54,059 --> 00:27:56,059
Then open it. Let's take a look.

455
00:27:56,061 --> 00:27:57,265
No, Your Majesty.

456
00:27:57,267 --> 00:27:58,782
- I will just...
- Why?

457
00:27:58,997 --> 00:28:00,425
