458
00:28:00,425 --> 00:28:02,510
But I'm shy.

459
00:28:09,818 --> 00:28:10,768
Did you...

460
00:28:12,503 --> 00:28:14,736
Did you really make this yourself?

461
00:28:17,113 --> 00:28:18,904
Do they look weird?

462
00:28:19,204 --> 00:28:21,597
It was my first time
so the shapes are...

463
00:28:21,597 --> 00:28:22,511
No.

464
00:28:23,409 --> 00:28:24,156
I thought...

465
00:28:25,722 --> 00:28:27,301
you were just a tomboy,

466
00:28:27,964 --> 00:28:29,065
but this is impressive.

467
00:28:30,526 --> 00:28:32,056
Do you mean that, Your Majesty?

468
00:28:33,394 --> 00:28:35,452
Are they okay?

469
00:28:35,725 --> 00:28:37,559
Not just okay.

470
00:28:39,097 --> 00:28:39,968
This is...

471
00:28:54,323 --> 00:28:55,836
What is it, Your Majesty?

472
00:28:58,284 --> 00:29:00,800
No... Well...

473
00:29:04,003 --> 00:29:06,170
Are you choking?

474
00:29:06,501 --> 00:29:08,222
Should I get you some water?

475
00:29:08,222 --> 00:29:09,278
No, it is okay.

476
00:29:11,066 --> 00:29:12,428
It is bearable.

477
00:29:15,028 --> 00:29:17,025
It is bearable?

478
00:29:17,433 --> 00:29:20,238
Goodness, does it taste that bad?

479
00:29:20,238 --> 00:29:21,935
Goodness, Your Majesty.

480
00:29:23,409 --> 00:29:24,356
Yeo Ji,

481
00:29:24,675 --> 00:29:26,077
did you not say...

482
00:29:26,933 --> 00:29:29,620
