before coming into the palace?

483
00:29:29,620 --> 00:29:31,840
Well, yes. I tried my best...

484
00:29:31,842 --> 00:29:33,513
You said your cooking skills...

485
00:29:34,362 --> 00:29:35,741
are much better...

486
00:29:37,159 --> 00:29:39,144
than the court ladies
in the royal kitchen.

487
00:29:39,735 --> 00:29:41,455
That is what I thought.

488
00:29:42,987 --> 00:29:44,472
That is what you thought?

489
00:29:45,738 --> 00:29:47,205
I am so sorry, Your Majesty.

490
00:29:47,207 --> 00:29:49,669
I will never do this again.

491
00:30:03,541 --> 00:30:04,740
Yes.

492
00:30:06,425 --> 00:30:07,880
This is what I liked...

493
