a fight with me.

506
00:31:01,222 --> 00:31:02,688
Am I correct?

507
00:31:08,269 --> 00:31:09,331
But you were wrong.

508
00:31:14,886 --> 00:31:16,047
I was not...

509
00:31:17,222 --> 00:31:19,132
trying to start a fight with you.

510
00:31:52,323 --> 00:31:53,309
This is...

511
00:32:03,816 --> 00:32:04,799
what I wanted to do.

512
00:32:10,113 --> 00:32:11,070
And...

513
00:32:21,450 --> 00:32:22,601
this.

514
00:32:35,355 --> 00:32:36,846
And I wanted...

515
00:32:40,980 --> 00:32:41,932
to always...

516
00:32:43,902 --> 00:32:45,478
