520
00:33:56,545 --> 00:33:57,780
What's going on?

521
00:33:57,780 --> 00:33:59,898
- What's happening?
- Is it really happening?

522
00:34:00,233 --> 00:34:01,741
- What was that?
- Oh no.

523
00:34:01,741 --> 00:34:03,243
What's going on?

524
00:34:05,380 --> 00:34:08,590
This is the house of rebel Lee
Yin Jwa's father-in-law.

525
00:34:10,069 --> 00:34:11,842
Letters or goods,

526
00:34:11,842 --> 00:34:13,223
