533
00:34:27,788 --> 00:34:29,202
Capture the offender!

534
00:34:29,202 --> 00:34:30,313
- Yes, master!
- Yes, master!

535
00:34:35,623 --> 00:34:36,879
What did you just say?

536
00:34:37,584 --> 00:34:39,908
