542
00:34:56,764 --> 00:34:57,609
Your Majesty.

543
00:34:57,611 --> 00:34:58,517
(Chief Corrector:
head of Saganwon)

544
00:34:58,542 --> 00:34:59,611
(Chief Professor:
head of Hongmoongwan)

545
00:34:59,655 --> 00:35:01,411
