546
00:35:01,811 --> 00:35:03,065
Should I still...

547
00:35:03,453 --> 00:35:05,239
listen to you?

548
00:35:14,405 --> 00:35:16,803
What's the current situation?

549
00:35:25,053 --> 00:35:26,181
Chief Justice.

550
00:35:32,873 --> 00:35:36,232
Execute the next order by the King.

551
00:35:36,234 --> 00:35:37,279
Yes, master.

552
00:35:40,077 --> 00:35:42,538
